FBIS4-46402 "jptot024__l94079" JPRS-TOT-94-024-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 10 June 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA IRAQ Explosion in Fuel Tank Truck in Baghdad District Reported Explosion in Fuel Tank Truck in Baghdad District Reported NC1006155394 (Clandestine) Voice of Iraqi Islamic Revolution in Arabic 1430 GMT 10 Jun 94 NC1006155394 (Clandestine) Voice of Iraqi Islamic Revolution in Arabic 1430 GMT 10 Jun 94 Arabic BFN [Text] Iraqi opposition sources in Baghdad have reported that an explosion took place on 28 May under a fuel tank truck in al-Rashidiyah district. The truck was completely destroyed after catching fire, and some people were injured. After the incident, security forces rushed to the area. They closed the roads leading to the incident and vacated the area of pedestrians.
